{"tid":1662523,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU連續三天傷心守靈，另一邊卻被網民攻擊。","createTime":"2019-10-18T21:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T04:07:24.000Z","uid":34643,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b00ed9f3a0562de42510f5b673f1dd067977aaf4","tid":1662523,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T21:47:06.000Z","msg":"【Sulli雪莉逝世】IU連續三天傷心守靈 粉絲勸停止惡言批評<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSulli離世後，不少藝人都在網上發文悼念。當中同屬f(x)一員的Krystal、Victoria宋茜及好友IU則因從來沒有發文而慘被網民攻擊，更迫使Victoria在微博反駁，希望大家不要再以社交媒體去判斷一個人，以及惡言能夠停止。IU早前宣布將暫停新專輯活動後，就再未有更新動向。不過今天不少韓國傳媒報道指，IU和Krystal一樣已連續三天在靈堂以傷心的心情守靈，只為送別及陪伴自己最好的姐妹。<br />\n<br />\nU守靈三天的新聞發佈後，不少粉絲非常擔心偶像連續痛失兩好友的心情，加上現時網上惡言滿天飛，因此大家都希望攻擊能夠立即停止。Sulli的離開使網絡霸凌的話題再次引來社會關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3425836/org/7275b4b907cced7904635576b8914331.jpg/UHjSgECFZ4bqip-pfSc2W4ygB4dX0cfiuRBrSrkQa0o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3425836%2Forg%2F7275b4b907cced7904635576b8914331.jpg%2FUHjSgECFZ4bqip-pfSc2W4ygB4dX0cfiuRBrSrkQa0o&h=072a34cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3425838/org/832d8e0c90bdca1781ec105cb0b3d87a.jpg/Lw0yS4JlBgnfe4xvGsDsGLmCjkb2BgGVOFnSxjhZ0sY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3425838%2Forg%2F832d8e0c90bdca1781ec105cb0b3d87a.jpg%2FLw0yS4JlBgnfe4xvGsDsGLmCjkb2BgGVOFnSxjhZ0sY&h=7e1305d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3425841/org/dabb989a3bbc5e1d241fb730f7d969ab.jpg/so5yQrq7ORN3vmzt9UCyV6utoG1nDtm9zG11pMxtdaQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3425841%2Forg%2Fdabb989a3bbc5e1d241fb730f7d969ab.jpg%2Fso5yQrq7ORN3vmzt9UCyV6utoG1nDtm9zG11pMxtdaQ&h=a5196bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3425840/